h3. Summary
Creating a JIRA backup (with attachments) of an Cloud instance, with a large number of attachments, take a very long time to complete.
Since Cloud instances are regularly restarted for maintenance, on week days, the backup process is interrupted, making it impossible to create these backups.


h3. Environment
* JIRA Cloud instance containing a large number of attachments

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# log into the instance
# go to the JIRA backup manager, https://<instance name>/plugins/servlet/ondemandbackupmanager/admin
# create a JIRA Server or Cloud backup with the attachments option checked

h3. Expected Results
A JIRA backup with attachments is created and available for download

h3. Actual Results
The JIRA backup with attachments is not created

The backup process is interrupted by the daily maintenance restart.
